<TITLE>
Wampanoag Language and the Wampanoag Indian Tribe (Massachusett, Natick, Massasoit, Nantucket) 
</TITLE>

<META NAME="description" CONTENT="Language, culture, history and genealogy of the Massachusett or Wampanoag Indians. Covers the Nantucket, Natick, Massasoit and Mashpee tribes.">
