">Wampanoag Glossary</a>:</b><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
List of Wampanoag words, compared to words in other Algonquian languages.
<BR>

<IMG SRC="dot5.gif"><b><A HREF="
http://www.bigorrin.org/waabu.htm
">Narragansett-Wampanoag Language Revival</a>:</b><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
Series of language revival articles, pronunciation and vocabulary charts by Dr. Frank Waabu O'Brien.
<BR>

<IMG SRC="dot5.gif"><b><A HREF="
http://www.native-languages.org/wampanoag_animals.htm
">Wampanoag Animal Words</a>:</b><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
Picture dictionary of animal words in the Wampanoag language.
<BR>

